      <title>哈萨克斯坦央行称市场押注欧洲央行降息 1-2 次，与基线一致</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/kazaks-says-market-bets-of-1-2-ecb-cuts-consistent-with-baseline</link>
